## Final Implementation Details

**Changes made to `lib/packages/packages/elements/src/elements/EFMedia.ts`:**
- Modified `fetchAudioSpanningTime()` method (lines ~897-980)
- Added conditional logic: `if (this.effectiveMode === "jit-transcode" && this.src)`
- JIT mode path:
  - Uses `this.jitTranscodingClient.fetchSegment()` for audio segments
  - Calculates segment boundaries based on 2s segment duration
  - Fetches multiple segments if the time range spans multiple segments
  - Combines all segments into a single blob
- Asset mode path: preserved original behavior unchanged

**Test coverage added:**
- Created `lib/packages/packages/elements/src/elements/EFMedia.test.ts` with comprehensive tests
- Tests cover both JIT and asset modes
- Validates URL patterns and audio data retrieval
- All tests passing ✅

